---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">About me</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">

  <i>Mildly extroverted, wildly opinionated,</i><br>
  chronically procrastinating—(<i>but hey, let’s call it intentional</i>).<br><br>

  I write when my brain won’t shut up—<br>
  sometimes thoughtful, sometimes just a rant with punctuation.<br><br>

  There’s a stethoscope somewhere in the background—<br>
  because, honestly, no med student ever <i><b>really</b></i> switches off. 
 </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="High school"
      subtitle="June 2022 to May 2024 at Narayani Model Secondary School, Bharatpur, Nepal "
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery (MBBS)"
      subtitle="December 2025 to Present at Pokhara Academy Of Health Sciences, Pokhara, Nepal  "
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

