      title="Volunteered for Awareness campaign regarding dignified menstruation"
  subtitle="From Jun 2024 to Nov 2024 at Miteri Jaibik Pad Udhyog, Chitwan, Nepal —  Assisted in menstrual health outreach, led awareness campaigns, and built brand presence. "
    >
 
    </TimeLineElement>
     
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="#" target="_blank"> Certification Name (with link)</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="#" target="_blank"> Certification Name (with link)</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>Community Engagement</li>
    <li>Teamwork</li>
    <li>Report Writing</li>
    <li>Verbal Storytelling</li>
